WITH STG AS(
SELECT 
    "Source / Medium",
    Year,
    CASE
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 1 THEN 'January'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 2 THEN 'Feburary'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 3 THEN 'March'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 4 THEN 'April'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 5 THEN 'May'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 6 THEN 'June'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 7 THEN 'July'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 8 THEN 'August'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 9 THEN 'September'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 10 THEN 'October'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 11 THEN 'November'
	WHEN "Month of the year" = 12 THEN 'December'
END AS month_of_the_year,
    REPLACE("Users",',','') AS Users,
    REPLACE("New Users",',','') AS New_Users,
    REPLACE(Sessions,',','') AS Sessions,
    REPLACE("Bounce Rate",'%','') AS Bounce_Rate,
    REPLACE(Pageviews, ',','') AS Pageviews,
    "Avg.Session Duration" AS Avg_Session_Duration,
   REPLACE("Conversion Rate (%)", '<0.01', '0.01') AS conversion_rate,
    REPLACE("Transactions", ',','') AS Transactions,
    REPLACE(Revenue, ',','') AS Revenue,
    REPLACE("Quantity Sold", ',','') AS Quantity_Sold
FROM 
    PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.Web_Analytics
)
SELECT * FROM STG

SELECT 
    Year,
    month_of_the_year,
    AVG(Bounce_Rate) AS Avg_bounce_rate,
    FROM 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_WEB__Web_Analytics
   GROUP BY Year, 
      month_of_the_year
  ORDER BY 
       Avg_bounce_rate DESC

SELECT 
    Year, 
    month_of_the_year,
  AVG(conversion_rate) AS Avg_conversion_rate
FROM 
    PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_WEB__Web_Analytics
GROUP BY Year, 
        month_of_the_year
ORDER BY Year,
    month_of_the_year

SELECT 
    Year,
     month_of_the_year, 
     users,
    LAG(users) OVER(ORDER BY Year, month_of_the_year) AS Previous_users,
    (users - LAG(users) OVER(ORDER BY Year, month_of_the_year)) /
    LAG(Users)  OVER(ORDER BY Year, month_of_the_year) * 100 AS Monthly_Growth_Rate
    From PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_WEB__Web_Analytics

SELECT 
        Year, 
        month_of_the_year,
    SUM(Pageviews)/SUM(Sessions) AS pageviews_per_sessions
FROM 
    PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_WEB__Web_Analytics
GROUP BY 
   Year,month_of_the_year
ORDER BY Year

SELECT
        Year, Month_of_the_Year,
        SUM(Users) as total_current_users,
        SUM(New_Users) as total_new_users,
        SUM(Sessions) as total_sessions
FROM
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_WEB__Web_Analytics
        GROUP BY Year, Month_of_the_Year
        ORDER BY Year

SELECT 
        sales_orders.sales_channel,
        sales_orders.procured_date,
        sales_orders.order_date,
        sales_orders.ship_date,
        sales_orders.delivery_date,
        sales_orders.team_id,
        sales_orders.customer_id,
        sales_orders.store_id,
        sales_orders.product_id,
        sales_orders.order_quantity,
        sales_orders.discount_applied,
        sales_orders.unit_price,
        sales_orders.unit_cost,
        customers.customer_names,
        products.product_name,
        store_locations.state,
        sales_team.team_name
FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_eCom__sales_orders sales_orders
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers customers ON sales_orders.customer_id = customers.customer_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products products ON sales_orders.product_id = products.product_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team sales_team ON sales_orders.team_id = sales_team.team_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_locations store_locations ON sales_orders.store_id = store_locations.store_id

SELECT
    AVG(DATEDIFF(DAY,Order_Date, Delivery_Date)) AS Average_Delivery_Day
FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales

SELECT 
        AVG(DATEDIFF(DAY, Order_Date, Ship_Date)) AS Average_shipping_days
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales

SELECT 
        customers.Customer_Names,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price - Unit_Cost) * Order_Quantity * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Profit_per_customer
    FROM 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sales_orders
    LEFT JOIN 
       PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS products ON products.product_id = sales_orders.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS customers ON customers.customer_id = sales_orders.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_locations AS store_locations ON store_locations.store_id = sales_orders.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        customers.Customer_Names
    ORDER BY 
        Profit_per_customer DESC

SELECT sales_team.team_name,
		sales_team.Team_ID,
		ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price*order_quantity) * (1-discount_applied)),0) AS Total_Revenue_by_sales_person
FROM 
		PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sales_order
LEFT JOIN 
	PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products products ON products.product_id = sales_order.product_id
LEFT JOIN 
	PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team sales_team ON  sales_team.team_id = sales_order.team_id

GROUP BY sales_team.team_name,
		sales_team.Team_ID
ORDER BY 
	Total_Revenue_by_sales_person DESC

SELECT 
        store_locations.state,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Revenue_Per_State
    FROM 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales AS sales_orders
    LEFT JOIN 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS products ON products.product_id = sales_orders.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS customers ON customers.customer_id = sales_orders.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_locations AS store_locations ON store_locations.store_id = sales_orders.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        store_locations.state
    ORDER BY 
        Revenue_Per_State DESC

SELECT sales_orders.Sales_Channel,
COUNT(Sales_Channel) AS Total_Orders_Per_Sales_Channels

SELECT 
        products.product_name,
        products.product_id,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Total_Product_Revenue
    FROM

    LEFT JOIN 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products  AS products ON products.product_id = sales_orders.product_id
    LEFT JOIN

    GROUP BY 
        products.product_name, products.product_id
